universe u

constant obj : Type u

constant BaldEagle : obj
constant Cow : obj
constant Rabbit : obj
constant Squirrel : obj

constant Chases : obj → obj → Prop
constant Red : obj → Prop
constant Sees : obj → obj → Prop
constant Eats : obj → obj → Prop
constant Nice : obj → Prop
constant Rough : obj → Prop
constant Round : obj → Prop
constant Kind : obj → Prop

axiom T1 : Chases BaldEagle Cow
axiom T2 : Red BaldEagle
axiom T3 : Sees BaldEagle Squirrel
axiom T4 : Chases Cow Rabbit
axiom T5 : Eats Cow Rabbit
axiom T6 : Red Cow
axiom T7 : Chases Rabbit Cow
axiom T8 : Eats Rabbit BaldEagle
axiom T9 : Nice Rabbit
axiom T10 : Rough Rabbit
axiom T11 : Eats Squirrel Cow
axiom T12 : Eats Squirrel Rabbit
axiom T13 : Nice Squirrel
axiom T14 : Sees Squirrel Rabbit

axiom R1 : ∀ x : obj, Chases x Squirrel → Chases Squirrel Cow
axiom R2 : ∀ x : obj, Chases x Squirrel ∧ Eats x Squirrel → Chases Squirrel Cow
axiom R3 : ∀ x : obj, Eats x Rabbit ∧ Rough x → Round x
axiom R4 : ∀ x : obj, Chases x Rabbit → Kind Rabbit
axiom R5 : ∀ x : obj, Kind x → Chases x Squirrel
axiom R6 : ∀ x : obj, Chases x Cow → Kind x
axiom R7 : ∀ x : obj, Eats x Rabbit ∧ ¬ Chases x Rabbit → Nice x

theorem squirrel_chases_squirrel : Chases Squirrel Squirrel :=
begin
  apply R5,
  apply R6,
  apply R1,
  apply R4,
  exact T4,
end
